er bound on the average mean-square reconstruction error.\nThe efficacy of the proposed schemes are demonstrated through numerical\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2015 08:40:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
