plementation of Omega that matches the necessary conditions we\nestablished.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2015 14:46:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 May 2015 23:03:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Feb 2016 14:39:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-15"}
